text.tspan: Informal employment in non-agricultural workplaces, by sex, 2023
Employment in the informal economy as a percentage of total non-agricultural employment, by sex. This
includes all jobs in unregistered and/or small-scale private unincorporated enterprises that produce goods or
services meant for sale or barter. Self-employed street vendors, taxi drivers and home-base workers,
regardless of size, are all considered enterprises.
